events.text: SG Julin Scarone was injured! (Patellar Tendinitis, out for 8 games)
GF Michel Ramos was injured! (Fractured Finger, out for 13 games)
SF Orland Moruga was injured! (Bruised Hip, out for 1 game)
SF Orland Moruga has recovered from his injury.

The Archivist Report #8: The Oakland Blue Oaks signed Veli-Matti Sinkkonen for $1M/year through 2024.
